message.body: This coat check probably works out well since you prefer to sleep late.
What's your schedule Sunday?
I hope so! I'm thinking my dysfunctional sleep schedule will benefit me some how. Maybe this is one of the ways I will reap the benefits :)
My friends and I were talking about going to Doylestown for an outing. You?
Trying to get people rock climbing. 3 head count currently
What a coincidence.
What is?
My friends want to go rock climbing in Doylestown.
Heh quite the coincidence.
So how was your day?
It was pleasant overall. I'm waiting for the EL at 11th. Et tu?
Wait, are you just getting out of work?
It was pretty chill.
No I went to the gym and took a class. It went longer than expected then I went to Chinatown for late dinner
Now waiting for train home. I missed my stop so I'm waiting for a train back lol. What a noob
Oh Okay. Fun day!
It's supposed to rain Friday. Maybe I can move my furniture on Saturday. You think you'll be sleeping regular or late tonight?
I don't even know what to tell you. I'm feeling pretty tired and sleepy right now, but I know I'm going to fight the urge.
So it might be a late brighter tonight.
If you can avoid getting your furniture wet, do it.
Where is it now? At your old place?
No it's at my parent's place.
You mind if I call for a bit?
Sure, if you still want to talk, feel free to call.
Ah that was last night. (Not that I don't want to talk) however I'm in the office now. Was gonna see if you were up to anything tonight.
Oh sorry, my phone was on silent mode. Didn't realize it until later. Yea, makes sense you'll be at work now hahah.
At the moment it'll be beer and pizza on south street.
I've never done st patty celebrations before but I don't think it'll be a crazy bar crawl.
Sorry if I kinda seemed like I was mumbling earlier. Didn't feel like blasting my business in the office.
Understandable. Thanks for the update! Are you wearing green today?
Not at work but I will be tonight!
